title: Managing Your Money - Ethereum's Big Gamble
description: The Ethereum network is going through a major upgrade that could turn it into the internet of crypto. Join Daren Fonda, managing editor at Barron's, and Sean Farrell, head of digital assets at Fundstrat Global  Advisors, to discuss what's ahead.
